😍Craving that golden, crispy bottom with a juicy soup-filled center? 

🧑🏻‍🍳🤩Here's how to pan-fry Synear Soup Dumplings to perfection:

1️⃣ Heat oil to 400°F and add the dumplings. Swirl to coat the bottoms evenly. 
2️⃣ Cover and fry for 3-5 minutes. 
3️⃣ Add a cup of water, cover, and steam for 5-7 minutes. 
4️⃣ Uncover and let the water evaporate, leaving the bottoms golden brown and irresistibly crispy (about 1-2 mins).

Plate, garnish with your favorite topping, and enjoy the ultimate comfort food! 😋✨ 

#soupdumplings #xiaolongbao #cozycomfortfood #panfrysoupdumplings #synearfoodsusa #aflavortoremember

Steaming soup dumplings, no bamboo steamer? No problem! 😎✨

With Synear, try these 3 hassle-free methods:

1️⃣ Stainless Steamer: Use it over a pot or pan with a lid, skip the steamer paper!
2️⃣ Rice Cooker: Steam with veggie 'paper' for no-stick perfection.
3️⃣ Rack + Plate: Air fryer/steam rack + flat plate = quick steaming hack.

#bamboosteamer #soupdumplings #xiaolongbao #synearfoodsusa #aflavortoremember

🥟 3 Steaming Mistakes to Avoid!
1️⃣ Don’t overcrowd — space = even cooking
2️⃣ Always wait for boiling water 
3️⃣ Steam 8–10 mins — not too short, not too long ⏱️

Perfect dumplings every time 😋

#DumplingTips #SteamingHacks #SynearUSA #SoupDumplings #KitchenTips #FoodieReels #HowToDumpling #SynearFoodsUSA #aflavortoremember

Easy Dumpling Soup 🥟

Craving takeout but don’t want to wait? This dumpling soup is faster, cozier, and comes together in just 15 minutes 

Start by sautéing 1 tbsp minced garlic and ½ cup chopped onion in a little oil, with salt, pepper, and garlic powder to taste. Add a bag of @synearfoodsusa frozen dumplings and let them get a bit crispy. Then pour in 8 cups of bone broth, 8 oz sliced mushrooms, 2 chopped pieces of bok choy, and 1 tbsp sesame oil. Let it simmer until everything’s tender and steamy.

So simple, so comforting, and honestly—better than takeout.

You can find @synearfoodsusa dumplings at Sam’s Club!

latestPosts.caption:
Soup dumplings but make it elevated ~🥟

These Thai red curry dumplings come together in 15 minutes using @synearfoodsusa juicy pork & cabbage dumplings—now at select @samsclub stores! #ad

Add a little coconut milk, curry paste, and you’ve got a flavor bomb of a weeknight dinner. 🥢

Tag a dumpling lover and run, don’t walk, to the freezer aisle! 🛒 

#thairedcurry #samsclubfinds #dumplinghack #comfortfoods 

Ingredients:
1 tbsp oil · 1 tbsp Thai red curry paste · 1 cup chicken stock · 1/3 cup coconut milk · 1 tsp fish sauce · 1 tsp sugar · 10 frozen Synear dumplings · Basil

Instructions:
Sauté curry paste in oil (2 min). Add stock and whisk smooth. Stir in coconut milk, fish sauce & sugar; simmer. Add dumplings, cover, and simmer 10 min. Garnish with basil & serve.
